    "body": "I should clarify this...I have _long_ stopped saying \"let's not fix the dashboard because we are about to do a big refactor.\" We have been doing incremental improvements to the dashboard for a while now. I remain +1 on that (after 4.0 and big split are done).\n\n@jdfreder already looked at fixing the Files tab scroll issue for the 3.0 release. At the time, we were still scrolling the entire page. With the whole page scroll, it was a complete mess to fix this for the Files tab while leaving the Running and Cluster tab the same. Now that we are back to scrolling just the site div, it may be easier - I had forgotten that the page doesn't scroll any longer.\n\nLet's see if some variant of the affix CSS class can get this to work.\n"
